  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali23-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu pirivuṇarttappaṭṭu āṟṟāḷāya talaivi emmaiyum uṭaṉ-koṇṭu ceṉmiṉeṉṟāṭku uṭaṉpaṭātu 
            avaṉ piriyaluṟat taṉatu iṟantupāṭutōṉṟak kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"/>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali23">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>ilaṅkoḷi maruppiṟ kaimmā vuḷampunar</l>
                <l>pulaṅkaṭi kavaṇaiyiṟ pūñciṉai yutirkku</l>
                <l>milaṅkumalai vempiya pōkkaru veñcuran</l>
                <l>taṉiyē yiṟappa yāṉoḻin tirutta</l>
                <l>ṉakutaṟ koṉṟiv vaḻuṅka lūrkkē;</l>
                <l rend="space">iṉiyāṉ,</l>
                <l>uṇṇalu muṇṇēṉ vāḻalum vāḻēṉ;</l>
                <l rend="space">tōṇala muṇṭu tuṟakkap paṭṭōr</l>
                <l>vēṇī ruṇṭa kuṭaiyō raṉṉar;</l>
                <l rend="space">nalkunar purintu nalaṉuṇap paṭṭō</l>
                <l>ralkunar pōkiya vūrō raṉṉar;</l>
                <l rend="space">kūṭiṉar purintu kuṇaṉuṇap paṭṭōr</l>
                <l>cūṭiṉa riṭṭa pūvō raṉṉar;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>yāṉu niṉṉakat taṉaiyē ṉāṉātu</l>
                <l>kolaiveṅ koḷkaiyoṭu nāyakap paṭuppa</l>
                <l>valaivark kamarnta maṭamāṉ pōla</l>
                <l>niṉṉāṅku varūumeṉ ṉeñciṉai</l>
                <l>yeṉṉāṅku vārā tōmpiṉai koṇmē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            Now, I </l>
<l>won’t eat at all and I won’t live at all,</l>
<l rend="space">Those who have been abandoned after the beauty of [their] shoulders has been consumed</l>
<l>they are just like baskets from which the coveted water has been drunk. </l>
<l rend="space">Those whose innocence has been consumed after someone who grants desired [it],</l>
<l>they are just like a village from which the inhabitants have gone.</l>
<l rend="space">Those whose quality has been consumed after someone who grants desired [it],</l>
<l>they are just like a flower put away by those who wore it.</l>
<l rend="space">That is to say,</l>
<l rend="space" corresp="15a-c">I too am like you inside. </l>
<l corresp="17">Like an innocent deer suited [to be caught] by those with nets, </l>
<l corresp="15d-16">while they unendingly control [their] dogs with the cruel tenet of killing, </l>
<l>take my heart that comes there to you</l>
<l corresp="18f">as one who has avoided coming there to me.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
